## Usage

0. If you haven't already, [go through the setup for the module](/setup).

1. Import the `{{kebab_case entry_type.name}}-summary` element somewhere in the javascript side of your web-app like this:

```js
import '@holochain-open-dev/{{kebab_case app_name}}/dist/elements/{{kebab_case entry_type.name}}-summary.js'
```

2. Use it in the html side of your web-app like this:

```html
<{{kebab_case entry_type.name}}-summary>
</{{kebab_case entry_type.name}}-summary>
```

> [!WARNING]
> Like all the elements in this module, `<{{kebab_case entry_type.name}}-summary>` needs to be placed inside an initialized `<{{kebab_case app_name}}-context>`.

